                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="â€¢ Open: 8:00 AM â€“ 5:00 PM\nâ€¢ Entry Fee: EGP 200 (foreigners), EGP 40 (locals)\nâ€¢ Best Time: October â€“ April\nâ€¢ Nearest Airport: Cairo International Airport (~30 km)"
